30:15.318 --> 30:17.401
[grunts]

30:26.068 --> 30:29.401
[Sandy] I don't trust those
fingerprint sensor locks.

30:29.484 --> 30:30.943
[door opens]

30:31.026 --> 30:32.235
[Daryll] Yeah, I know
what you mean.

30:32.318 --> 30:34.151
They won't be getting
