be in cahoots with each other.

30:42.734 --> 30:44.567
Oh, man, Mickey,
what are you doing?

30:44.651 --> 30:46.526
I should shoot
the both of yous.

30:46.609 --> 30:49.651
I saw my chance,
and I took it, Mick.

30:49.734 --> 30:52.235
[scoffs]
You would have done the same.

30:52.318 --> 30:53.943
And why the hell
are you dressed

30:54.026 --> 30:55.734
in your brother's clothes?

30:55.818 --> 30:58.526
I haven't touched those clothes
since the day he died.

30:58.609 --> 31:01.235
Yeah, you're a real
sentimental bitch.

31:01.318 --> 31:04.318
Tell me about it.

31:04.401 --> 31:06.943
I need a fucking drink.

31:09.276 --> 31:11.776
Pop, listen to me.

31:11.859 --> 31:13.235
Okay, you got to know

31:13.318 --> 31:16.193
