was going to kill you.

31:16.276 --> 31:18.984
All right, I saved your life.
I mean, you have to know that.

31:19.068 --> 31:21.360
Jesus Christ, I mean,
you're the one who went

31:21.442 --> 31:23.776
and blackmailed Jay White
into making a movie.

31:23.859 --> 31:28.401
Like, I was fine.
I was okay working with Ray.

31:28.484 --> 31:30.442
And you think this
makes it all right?

31:30.526 --> 31:33.193
What an asshole.
Who do you think I am?

31:33.276 --> 31:36.151
That's some twisted
fucking understanding.

31:36.235 --> 31:38.776
What you did was foul.
You betrayed your own father.

31:38.859 --> 31:40.110
It was Ray.

31:41.360 --> 31:42.734
Fuck Ray.

31:42.818 --> 31:46.567
Pop, he said you--
you would rat me out,

31:46.651 --> 31:49.193
that you were gonna talk.

31:49.276 --> 31:51.734
That's the one thing
I would never do,

31:51.818 --> 31:53.692
is rat on my own family.

31:56.901 --> 32:00.484
Even knowing that I might
never get out of that jail,

32:00.567 --> 32:04.442
that I would die there,
I didn't rat you out.

32:05.943 --> 32:08.026
I never said one word.

32:08.110 --> 32:10.901
I never would, see?

32:10.984 --> 32:12.360
That's who I am.

32:17.276 --> 32:21.360
But I done
enough bad shit, so...

32:21.442 --> 32:25.110
So here we are--
the scumbag reunion.

32:29.318 --> 32:31.651
Now, where's
my fucking money, Sandy?

32:31.734 --> 32:33.151
[Sandy] Brendan's got it.

32:33.235 --> 32:35.692
I gave it back.

32:35.776 --> 32:36.943
Hey, hey, Pop.

32:37.026 --> 32:38.943
Can I get a cut of that?

32:39.026 --> 32:41.318
No, you don't get a cut.

32:41.401 --> 32:43.943
The person who pays the ransom
doesn't get a portion

32:44.026 --> 32:46.235
of the fucking ransom.

32:46.318 --> 32:49.401
[cell phone clicking]

32:56.442 --> 32:59.360
♪ dramatic music ♪

32:59.442 --> 33:04.567
