33:17.692 --> 33:19.442
Get out of the car.

33:21.526 --> 33:23.442
It's a long story, Ray.

33:24.651 --> 33:26.692
Get out
of the fucking car, Bunch.

33:38.734 --> 33:41.609
Where's the money, Bunch?

33:41.692 --> 33:43.901
I'm taking it.

33:43.984 --> 33:46.235
I got to do something right
for a change.

33:46.318 --> 33:48.026
Do it for my family.

33:50.484 --> 33:53.943
- Where's the money, Bunch?
- You can't have it, Ray.

33:54.026 --> 33:55.484
Where's the fucking money?

33:55.567 --> 33:58.442
You can't have it.
It's mine.

33:58.526 --> 34:01.193
[Bunchy] You can't
fucking have it.

34:01.276 --> 34:02.776
No, you don't--No.

34:02.859 --> 34:05.110
No, you can't have it.
You can't--

34:05.193 --> 34:06.484
It's for my family!

34:06.567 --> 34:09.110
No, damn--no!

34:09.193 --> 34:11.110
Fuck--
No, no, no!

34:11.193 --> 34:13.609
No, no!
You fucking--

34:13.692 --> 34:15.567
♪♪♪

34:15.651 --> 34:18.026
You can't have it!

34:18.110 --> 34:21.318
[grunting]

34:21.401 --> 34:26.484
♪♪♪

34:33.026 --> 34:35.943
[engine turning over, revs]

34:36.026 --> 34:40.859
♪♪♪

34:42.692 --> 34:45.360
[cash counting machine
clicking rapidly]

34:45.442 --> 34:48.609
♪♪♪

34:48.692 --> 34:51.526
[machine beeps]

34:54.609 --> 34:57.193
Ray.

34:57.276 --> 34:59.859
Vinny.
Vinny, Ray.

34:59.943 --> 35:02.776
[gasps] Oh, you gentlemen
have already met.

35:05.859 --> 35:07.526
