35:11.651 --> 35:15.068
Are you talking
about your prostitute friend?

35:16.360 --> 35:19.943
You're the one that--that
made her lie on national TV,

35:20.026 --> 35:24.151
and then you were the one
that humiliated her afterwards.

35:24.235 --> 35:26.401
I didn't have a choice.

35:28.943 --> 35:30.901
Are you saying I did?

35:34.526 --> 35:36.609
[whispering]
Listen, Ray...

35:36.692 --> 35:40.526
if it weren't for the things
that you did,

35:40.609 --> 35:43.068
that woman
would still be alive.

35:45.526 --> 35:47.193
You think about that.

35:47.276 --> 35:49.526
♪ dramatic music ♪

35:49.609 --> 35:51.401
You should have
let me handle it.

35:51.484 --> 35:52.859
♪♪♪

35:52.943 --> 35:54.734
I did.

35:54.818 --> 35:59.692
♪♪♪

36:06.651 --> 36:09.567
[cell phone rings]

36:09.651 --> 36:13.984
♪♪♪

36:14.068 --> 36:16.235
Hey, sweetheart.

36:20.943 --> 36:24.110
Now?

36:24.193 --> 36:26.692
All right, I'll get there
as soon as I can.

36:30.318 --> 36:32.235
[cell phone beeps]

36:35.526 --> 36:39.442
[car horns honking]

36:42.360 --> 36:44.901
[indistinct chatter]

36:44.984 --> 36:45.901
Hey.

36:45.984 --> 36:47.318
Hey.

36:51.401 --> 36:53.442
You all right?

36:59.360 --> 37:01.818
