37:07.859 --> 37:09.734
Why?

37:11.984 --> 37:13.193
No, I didn't.

37:13.276 --> 37:14.901
Yes, you did.

37:14.984 --> 37:16.901
Why?

37:19.442 --> 37:21.318
What's going on, Bridge?

37:21.401 --> 37:23.318
Please answer me.

37:26.484 --> 37:30.110
I don't know.
Maybe, uh...

37:30.193 --> 37:32.110
